items.title: Q3 results this week: SBI, ITC, LIC among 748 companies to announce earnings
items.description: This week, 748 companies will announce quarterly earnings, with key results expected from Asian Paints, Titan, Airtel, SBI, M&M, ITC, and LIC. Sector highlights include Power Grid, Divi's Labs, Tata Power, and Bharti Airtel, among others. Notable earnings announcements span from February 3 to February 8, indicating a busy week for the markets.
